 1→//! GraphQL API for Moltis.
 2→//!
 3→//! Provides a typed GraphQL schema that mirrors the RPC interface, exposing
 4→//! queries, mutations, and subscriptions for all gateway services. The schema
 5→//! is served at `/graphql` (GraphiQL on GET, queries on POST, subscriptions via
 6→//! WebSocket upgrade on GET).
 7→//!
 8→//! Resolvers call domain services directly through the `Services` bundle from
 9→//! `moltis-service-traits`, sharing the same code path as the RPC layer. No
10→//! string-based dispatch or RPC indirection is used.
11→//!
12→//! The gateway crate is responsible for building the HTTP handlers and wiring
13→//! them into the router. This crate only defines the schema, types, and resolvers.
14→
